<li role="presentation"><a href='https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/nlmcatalog?term="Proc%20Natl%20Acad%20Sci%20U%20S%20A"[Title%20Abbreviation]' class="usa-link" role="menuitem">View in NLM Catalog</a></li>
